4 ofercumen wurde se heardnes þe me hæfð
5 utan berytled fram ðæm beorhtan eowde,
6 feond ðæm wulfum þe him winnende sind;

7 mid oðerre stemne nu, mid oðrum gyrlum,
8 ic gewende eft scôp, and æt ðæm wylle
9 mines fulluhtes ic ðone chapeau onfo;

13 Þa com leoht neawest us
14 of ðære sphere ðanon com seo frumcenned
15 ðe Crist læfde of his vicarium;

70 Of manega steorran me ðeos leohte becymð;
71 ac he ða on ðam breostan minum ær gesette
72 ða he wæs ðara leoda sumes wealdendes scop.

91 Cwæð Isaías ðæt ælc ymbwrigen
92 on his eðle bið mid twyfealdan hrægle:
93 and his eðel is ðeos swetnysse;

97 And ærrest, æfter ðæra worda ende,
98 ‘Hyht in ðe’ ofer us we gehyrdon;
99 ðæm andswaredon ealle ða weras.

109 He hine ðær gesette on ðone ende and on ðæt hweol;
110 and min lafdi heold ðær on ða hire gesihoe,
111 swa swa bryd ðuguðe and gestille.

118 Swylce se ðe ðone sunnan onwlitan wile
119 ðurh ðone ðe he ðone ðeostran gesihð,
120 ðæt he ðurh ðæt gesihð ðæt gesiho forlyst;

127 Mid ðam twam stolum on ðam beorhtan clystre
128 synd ða twegen sunnan ðe ðær upp astah;
129 and ðis ðu gebringst on eowre woruld."
